Maintainer: Alexander Wireko Kena <alex.kena24@gmail.com>
Description: Make genetic crosses for diploid species and visualize genotypes of
    progenies in a Punnett square. It allows users to visualize phenotypic predictions 
    for basic classical genetics hypotheses on gene action and allele interactions.
